# Mobile-drawer drift fix — the base template ships the OLD children-based
# sidebar-toggle.tsx, but _header-with-defaults.tsx (template + production)
# passes SidebarTree data props (nodes/currentSlug/rootMenuItems/...) to
# <SidebarToggle>. The old component ignored them and rendered `{children}`
